---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to William Sutton's Blog</h1>
			<p>
				Hey there! I'm William Sutton, and this is where I talk about UK politics. I love diving into the latest political happenings and trends, and I'm here to share my thoughts and analyses with you.
			</p>
			<p>
				I take a close look at current events and political issues, offering my unique take on everything. Whether it's breaking news or deep dives into policy and ideology, I aim to keep things interesting and thought-provoking.
			</p>
			<p>
				This blog is all about independent thinking and open discussion, without the usual mainstream media spin. I hope you'll join in and share your views on the fascinating world of UK politics.
			</p>
			<p>
				Have a look around and check out the articles and posts. If you've got any questions or just want to chat, don't hesitate to reach out.
			</p>
			<p>
				Thanks for stopping by! I hope you enjoy the content and find it both informative and engaging.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>